column5: This is a news story about ice safety...and the news van goes thru the ice.....

WELL I THINK THAT WILL BE COMMING OUT OF HIS PAY FOR A LONG,LONG TIME....THOSE SATELLITE NEWS VANS ARE WORTH ABOUT $90.000 ....HES GONNA NEED A UNION REP FOR HIS MEETING WITH THE BOSS THE NEXT DAY...LOL...LOL
Now that's LIVE reporting.  "Watch me drive over the ice.   Kinds ... do not try this at home"
Bonehead move.  Doing a story on dangers of thin ice and go through yourself.
Im thinking of a quote from that 70's show, made by Mr. Red Foreman himself...
